				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/Du-th%C3%A0nh-nam-th%E1%BA%ADp-l%E1%BB%A5c-th%E1%BB%A7-Ph%C3%B9-di%E1%BB%85m/poem-SvsCWh5k2cREsq3kDzZKog">Du thành nam thập lục thủ - Phù diễm - 遊城南十六首－浮艷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/author-mXDKUZpgHTE66OhltBCLIw">Hàn Dũ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C6%B0u-Ki%E1%BB%87u/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-li%E1%BB%85u-chi-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-jWReqsh-OvE3-674QW3RBg">Dương liễu chi kỳ 4 - 楊柳枝其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C6%B0u-Ki%E1%BB%87u/author-HGXscoFVRX97F-vnBz6XUQ">Ngưu Kiệu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-L%E1%BB%8Bch-tam-ni%C3%AAn-xu%C3%A2n-B%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%E1%BA%BF-th%C3%A0nh-ph%C3%B3ng-thuy%E1%BB%81n-xu%E1%BA%A5t-C%C3%B9-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-gi%C3%A1p-c%E1%BB%ADu-c%C6%B0-Qu%E1%BB%B3-Ph%E1%BB%A7-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%C3%ADch/poem-FdJ4yvYyTSKfMStGhGDgGg">Đại Lịch tam niên xuân Bạch Đế thành phóng thuyền xuất Cù Đường giáp, cửu cư Quỳ Phủ tương thích Giang Lăng phiêu bạc, hữu thi phàm tứ thập vận - 大歷三年春白帝城放船出瞿唐峽久居夔府將適江陵漂泊有詩凡四十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81n-Th%C3%B9/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1p-sa-h%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-u5WjfJnZpgfN3j7e3jgKPg">Đạp sa hành kỳ 4 - 踏莎行其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81n-Th%C3%B9/author-vOEpptlMHWVC0_k_NsTzRg">Án Thù</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%E1%BB%99t/%C4%90%E1%BA%B1ng-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-c%C3%A1c-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-FT3LNnXR5KVN9HD70_hBOw">Đằng Vương các tự - 滕王閣序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%E1%BB%99t/author-_ZqxSvkbsUwNbnMEINI85Q">Vương Bột</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/Hi%E1%BA%BFn-Phong-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-phu-ph%C3%A1-B%C3%A1-Ti%C3%AAn-kh%E1%BA%A3i-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-tiqrhz1edmtaLOu8B9tUZA">Hiến Phong đại phu phá Bá Tiên khải ca kỳ 2 - 獻封大夫破播仙凱歌其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/author-AcWs16LhWAEAw513Kk2DnA">Sầm Tham</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/H%E1%BB%B1u-tr%C3%ACnh-Ng%C3%B4-lang/poem-55UuAXSytRBoeKCNG2NozA">Hựu trình Ngô lang - 又呈吳郎</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAu-Khoan/Sinh-tra-t%E1%BB%AD-T%C3%ACnh-c%E1%BA%A3nh/poem-zFVLMen3oK-wvMbMOgwbkg">Sinh tra tử - Tình cảnh - 生查子－情景</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAu-Khoan/author-ryoCFWRVKVZLaDuFv6ToUg">Diêu Khoan</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%C3%A0nh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i/Th%C3%B4i-t%C3%B4-h%C3%A0nh/poem-gmB1n6my6IUHsIlOzc-dWQ">Thôi tô hành - 催租行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%C3%A0nh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i/author-ppK7YKfOyDZw9vIHLHbJVA">Phạm Thành Đại</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%B4ng-ph%E1%BA%A5t-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-AVg8Skt8920Y3Be0N6PH8Q">Tông phất tử - 棕拂子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
